name: VIVA INFERNO - Canto 1 (In the dark forest)
description:
"Midway upon the journey of our life I found myself within a forest dark,
⁠For the straightforward pathway had been lost.
Ah me! how hard a thing it is to say
⁠What was this forest savage, rough, and stern, 
⁠Which in the very thought renews the fear."
First Canto (In the dark forest) from one of the first Narrative Collectible Series in NFT History.
Viva Inferno ist the digital Reconstruction of Dantes Divine Comedy.
JPEG/STILL 300 DPI, 4622 x 6666 px
